#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:2
msgid "产品设置（Recipe）"
msgstr "Product Recipe"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:4
msgid ""
"产品设置区（**设置**，即 Recipe）位于编程页面（Teach）左侧标签栏的顶部区域。该区域包含五个子标签，用于配置产品的传送带、PCB "
"物理参数及检测判废逻辑。子标签依次为："
msgstr ""
"The product setup area — **Recipe** — sits at the top of the left-hand tab "
"strip on the Teach page. It contains five sub-tabs for configuring the "
"conveyor, PCB physical parameters, and inspection verdict logic. The sub-"
"tabs are, in order:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:6
msgid "**PCB详情** （PCB Detail）"
msgstr "**PCB Detail**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:7
msgid "**传送带设置** （Conveyor Setup）"
msgstr "**Conveyor Setup**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:8
msgid "**PCB尺寸** （PCB Dimension）"
msgstr "**PCB Dimension**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:9
msgid "**全PCB拍摄** （Full PCB Capture）"
msgstr "**Full PCB Capture**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:10
msgid "**检测设置** （Inspection Settings）"
msgstr "**Inspection Settings**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:12
msgid "每个子标签完成后会显示蓝色对勾图标，表示该步骤已配置完成。后四个子标签在完成前置步骤之前处于禁用状态，须按顺序操作。"
msgstr ""
"A blue check icon appears next to a sub-tab once that step is complete. The "
"last four sub-tabs are disabled until their prerequisite step is done — work"
" through them in order."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:-1
msgid "设置区五个子标签栏（PCB详情 / 传送带设置 / PCB尺寸 / 全PCB拍摄 / 检测设置）"
msgstr ""
"The Recipe area's five sub-tabs: PCB Detail / Conveyor Setup / PCB Dimension"
" / Full PCB Capture / Inspection Settings"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:20
msgid "**PCB详情（PCB Detail）**"
msgstr "**PCB Detail**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:22
msgid "PCB详情标签页包含两个区域："
msgstr "The PCB Detail tab has two areas:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:24
msgid ""
"**产品名称（产品名称）**：可在此输入或修改产品名称。产品名称须唯一；若与已有产品重名，保存时会提示错误。点击 **保存** 提交修改，点击 "
"**取消** 放弃编辑。"
msgstr ""
"**Product Name**: enter or rename the product here. The name must be unique;"
" saving a duplicate name shows an error. Click **Save** to commit, "
"**Cancel** to discard the edit."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:26
msgid "**检测参数（Specs for Inspection）**：以列表形式显示四项产品参数的当前状态，每项均有操作按钮可跳转至对应子标签页："
msgstr ""
"**Specs for Inspection**: lists the current state of four product "
"parameters; each row carries an action button that jumps to the "
"corresponding sub-tab:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:28
msgid ""
"**传送带宽度（Conveyor Width）**：未设置时显示 ``(未定义)``，已设置时显示毫米数值。点击 **设置** 跳转至 "
"**传送带设置** 子标签。"
msgstr ""
"**Conveyor Width**: shows ``(undefined)`` when unset, the value in "
"millimeters when set. Click **Set** to jump to **Conveyor Setup**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:29
msgid ""
"**PCB尺寸（PCB Dimension）**：未测量时显示 ``(未定义)``，已测量时显示宽 × 高（mm）。点击 **测量** 跳转至 "
"**PCB尺寸** 子标签。"
msgstr ""
"**PCB Dimension**: shows ``(undefined)`` when unmeasured, width × height "
"(mm) once measured. Click **Measure** to jump to **PCB Dimension**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:30
msgid ""
"**全PCB拍摄（Full PCB Capture）**：未拍摄时显示 ``(未定义)``，已拍摄时显示已采集状态。点击 **拍摄** 跳转至 "
"**全PCB拍摄** 子标签。"
msgstr ""
"**Full PCB Capture**: shows ``(undefined)`` when not yet captured, "
"*captured* once acquired. Click **Capture** to jump to **Full PCB Capture**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:31
msgid ""
"**检测设置（Inspection Settings）**：显示当前判废模式摘要（见下方说明）。点击 **配置** 跳转至 **检测设置** 子标签。"
msgstr ""
"**Inspection Settings**: shows a summary of the current verdict mode (see "
"below). Click **Configure** to jump to **Inspection Settings**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:-1
msgid "PCB详情标签页：产品名称、检测参数四行（传送带宽度 / PCB尺寸 / 全PCB拍摄 / 检测设置）"
msgstr ""
"PCB Detail tab: Product Name plus four Specs-for-Inspection rows (Conveyor "
"Width / PCB Dimension / Full PCB Capture / Inspection Settings)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:39
msgid "**传送带设置（Conveyor Setup）**"
msgstr "**Conveyor Setup**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:41
msgid "传送带设置用于在编程过程中锁定传送带并调整宽度，以便手动放板或使用 PCB 进入功能。"
msgstr ""
"Conveyor Setup locks the conveyor for the programming session and adjusts "
"its width so you can load boards manually or use PCB In."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:43
msgid "操作步骤："
msgstr "Steps:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:45
msgid "**选择一个传送带（Select a Conveyor）**：从下拉列表中选择当前可用的传送带槽位。"
msgstr ""
"**Select a Conveyor**: pick an available conveyor slot from the drop-down."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:46
msgid "**锁定传送带（Lock Conveyor for this Task）**：点击此按钮锁定所选传送带供本次编程使用。"
msgstr ""
"**Lock Conveyor for this Task**: click to claim the selected conveyor for "
"this programming session."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:47
msgid ""
"**设置传送带宽度（Set Conveyor Width）**：在输入框中输入目标宽度（mm），再点击 **移动到宽度（Move to Width）**"
" 使传送带实际移动到该宽度。当前传送带宽度会显示在下方以供参考。"
msgstr ""
"**Set Conveyor Width**: enter the target width (mm), then click **Move to "
"Width** to drive the conveyor to that width. The current width is shown "
"below for reference."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:48
msgid ""
"**保存并继续（Save and Continue）**：确认宽度后点击此按钮，将宽度写入产品并跳转至 **PCB尺寸** "
"子标签。需已完成锁定方可启用。"
msgstr ""
"**Save and Continue**: after confirming the width, click to write it into "
"the product and jump to **PCB Dimension**. Enabled only after the conveyor "
"is locked."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:49
msgid "**释放传送带（Release Conveyor）**：操作完成后点击此按钮，释放对传送带的独占控制权。"
msgstr ""
"**Release Conveyor**: when you're done, click to release the exclusive lock."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:-1
msgid "传送带设置步骤：选择传送带 + 锁定 / 释放传送带按钮、进板 / 出板"
msgstr ""
"Conveyor Setup steps: Select a Conveyor + Lock / Release buttons + PCB In / "
"PCB Out"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:57
msgid "**PCB尺寸（PCB Dimension）**"
msgstr "**PCB Dimension**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:59
msgid ""
"该标签页用于测量或输入 PCB 的物理尺寸（宽度与高度，单位 mm）。操作流程与创建产品向导中的 **输入或计算尺寸** 步骤一致，详见 "
":ref:`创建产品` 中的对应说明。"
msgstr ""
"This sub-tab measures or accepts the PCB's physical dimensions (width and "
"height, in millimeters). The workflow is the same as the **Enter or "
"Calculate Dimension** step in the Create-Product wizard; see :ref:`创建产品` for"
" details."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:65
msgid "**全PCB拍摄（Full PCB Capture）**"
msgstr "**Full PCB Capture**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:67
msgid ""
"该标签页用于重新执行完整 PCB 拍摄，生成用于检测的黄金图像。操作流程与创建产品向导中的 **完整 PCB 拍摄** 步骤一致，详见 "
":ref:`创建产品` 中的对应说明。完成拍摄后可在此处更新相机参数（曝光、增益、白平衡等）并重新拍摄覆盖当前版本。"
msgstr ""
"This sub-tab re-captures the full PCB to produce the golden image used "
"during inspection. The workflow is the same as the **Full PCB Capture** step"
" in the Create-Product wizard; see :ref:`创建产品` for details. After capture, "
"you can adjust camera parameters here (exposure, gain, white balance, and so"
" on) and re-capture to overwrite the current version."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:73
msgid "**检测设置（Inspection Settings）**"
msgstr "**Inspection Settings**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:75
msgid "检测设置标签页用于配置拼板产品中 **子板（sub-PCB）** 的自动判废逻辑，决定系统如何判断每块子板为好板或坏板。"
msgstr ""
"The Inspection Settings sub-tab configures automatic verdict logic for "
"**sub-boards** in a PCB Array (panel) product — how the system decides each "
"sub-board is good or bad."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:77
msgid "可从 PCB详情 标签页点击 **检测设置** 行右侧的 **配置** 按钮进入此标签页。"
msgstr ""
"Reach this sub-tab from PCB Detail by clicking **Configure** on the "
"Inspection Settings row."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:79
msgid "该标签页包含以下四项参数："
msgstr "Four parameters are exposed:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:81
msgid "**使用NG元件比例（Use NG component ratio）**"
msgstr "**Use NG component ratio**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:83
msgid "Switch 开关，默认 **开启**。启用后，系统根据子板上 NG 元件的比例来自动判废。开启时，下方显示以下子项："
msgstr ""
"Switch; default **on**. When enabled, the system auto-fails a sub-board "
"based on the proportion of NG components on it. Exposes:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:85
msgid ""
"**失败比例阈值（Failure ratio threshold）**：InputNumber 输入框，有效范围 ``0.0–1.0``，默认值 "
"``0.5``。当子板的 NG 元件比例超过该阈值时，子板被判定为坏板。"
msgstr ""
"**Failure ratio threshold**: numeric input, range ``0.0–1.0``, default "
"``0.5``. A sub-board is judged bad when its NG-component ratio exceeds this "
"threshold."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:87
msgid "**使用坏板标记元件（Use badmark elements）**"
msgstr "**Use badmark elements**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:89
msgid ""
"Switch 开关，默认 **关闭**。启用后，系统依据产品中已定义的坏板标记元件（badmark）来判废子板（参见 "
":ref:`检测控制与特殊标记`）。开启时，下方显示以下子项："
msgstr ""
"Switch; default **off**. When enabled, the system uses the product's defined"
" badmark components to decide each sub-board (see :ref:`检测控制与特殊标记`). "
"Exposes:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:91
msgid "**组合逻辑（Combine logic）**：Radio 单选，可选："
msgstr "**Combine logic**: radio buttons; choose:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:93
msgid "**任一NG**：只要有任意一个坏板标记元件判为 NG，子板即判为坏板。"
msgstr "**Any NG**: the sub-board is bad if any badmark component is NG."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:94
msgid "**全部NG**：所有坏板标记元件均判为 NG，子板才判为坏板。"
msgstr ""
"**All NG**: the sub-board is bad only when every badmark component is NG."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:96
msgid "**已定义坏板标记元件数（Badmark elements defined）**：显示当前产品中已定义的坏板标记元件数量（只读）。"
msgstr ""
"**Badmark elements defined**: read-only count of badmark components "
"currently defined in the product."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:98
msgid "若启用了坏板标记模式但尚未定义任何坏板标记元件，页面会显示黄色警告提示，说明该模式不会生效。"
msgstr ""
"When the badmark mode is on but no badmark components are defined, a yellow "
"warning explains that the mode will have no effect."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:100
msgid "**两种模式均关闭时**"
msgstr "**When both modes are off**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:102
msgid "若 **使用NG元件比例** 和 **使用坏板标记元件** 均关闭，页面会显示提示信息：子板不会被自动判定，仅进行人工复检。"
msgstr ""
"If both **Use NG component ratio** and **Use badmark elements** are off, the"
" page shows a notice: sub-boards will not be auto-judged — manual review "
"only."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:104
msgid "**保存与取消**"
msgstr "**Save and Cancel**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:106
msgid ""
"编辑完成后点击 **保存** 提交修改；点击 **取消** 恢复为上次已保存的值。提交前系统会校验 **失败比例阈值** 是否在 ``[0, 1]`` "
"范围内，超出范围将提示错误并阻止保存。"
msgstr ""
"Click **Save** to commit; click **Cancel** to revert to the last saved "
"values. Before saving, the system checks that **Failure ratio threshold** is"
" in ``[0, 1]`` and blocks the save with an error if it isn't."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:108
msgid "**PCB详情中的检测设置状态摘要**"
msgstr "**Inspection Settings status summary on PCB Detail**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:110
msgid "PCB详情标签页的 **检测设置** 行会根据当前配置显示以下摘要文字："
msgstr ""
"The Inspection Settings row on PCB Detail shows one of the following "
"summaries:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:112
msgid "**比例 · 坏板标记**：两种模式均已启用。"
msgstr "**Ratio · Badmark**: both modes are enabled."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:113
msgid "**仅比例**：仅启用了NG元件比例模式。"
msgstr "**Ratio only**: only the NG-component-ratio mode is enabled."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:114
msgid "**仅坏板标记**：仅启用了坏板标记模式。"
msgstr "**Badmark only**: only the badmark mode is enabled."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:115
msgid "**仅人工复检**：两种模式均已关闭。"
msgstr "**Manual review only**: both modes are disabled."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/recipe.rst:-1
msgid "检测设置标签页：使用NG元件比例开关、失败比例阈值、使用坏板标记元件开关"
msgstr ""
"Inspection Settings sub-tab: Use NG component ratio switch, Failure ratio "
"threshold, Use badmark elements switch"
